conversation_history.content: Hi Ethan! If you could fast forward to 2-5 years from now, what long term goal / goals do you have? This could be anything from getting accepted into a dream university, launching your own startup, or becoming a successful practitioner in a field you're passionate about.
I want to get into a top 10 US university, that's my main goal!

Great! I can see you're focused on top 10 university acceptance. Would you like to share some of your extracurricular activities and experiences that relate to these goals? This will help me give you more targeted advice.
Yes, I'd like to share my extracurriculars
Perfect! Please add your extracurricular activities one at a time. For each activity, provide a title and description.
Are you considering taking on a leadership role or initiating a project within the UBC Laboratory to further develop your research skills?
Thanks for sharing! Let's identify some specific next steps to strengthen your profile.
Are you considering taking on a leadership role or initiating a project within the UBC Laboratory to further develop your research skills?
no not really I don't want to continue with the lab it was a one time thing. I want to look for other related opportunities though
Would you like assistance in crafting compelling essays that highlight your unique experiences and aspirations for your university applications?
Are you interested in securing another internship, perhaps in a different area of software engineering or AI application?
yes, I'd love that as well
